tests so if you want to write

00:00:54.270 --> 00:00:55.739
integration tests and if you are using

00:00:55.739 --> 00:00:57.600
spring in your application go ahead and

00:00:57.600 --> 00:01:00.359
don't mock then it will start calling

00:01:00.359 --> 00:01:02.430
into the next layer you have to make

00:01:02.430 --> 00:01:04.739
sure all the dependencies are correct

